abstracts.cdata!:
The project consists of a program to
            help finance the development, over a period of 5 years, of
            new or improved market facilities in Mysore. The facilities
            to be provided include access roads, auction platforms,
            fencing, buildings, traders' shop-cum-godowns, internal
            roadways, parking areas, utilities and ancillary equipment.
            The project will also provide for training of marketing
            personnel and for project evaluation.
